\nw[Taro](If I remember correctly, the monster broke
through the ship's wall and pulled Shia into the
sea, and I tried to save her... I'm pretty sure I
defeated the monster.)

\nw[Taro](After that, we somehow managed to swim and aim
for the island... It seems like we lost
consciousness...)

\nw[Taro](How did we end up here? It's not like Shia can
swim... Was it just incredible luck?)

\nw[Taro]It's only natural since we were in the sea... How
can we warm up...

\nw[Taro]Prae!? Oh right, she can communicate and see
what's happening over here.

\nw[Prae's voice]For now, let's just snuggle up to that person.
Even if they complain, we'll figure something out
later. That's how we'll listen to their story.
\nw[Taro]Shia, I'm going to hug you for a bit...

\nw[Taro]No, there should be someone I can communicate
with. I'm pretty sure they could see what was
happening with me, Kuno, and Nonna.

\nw[Shia]I see... Ugh... We won't warm up right away,
huh...

\nw[Taro](Even when I hug her, she doesn't react at all...
Is it because her body is cold, or is it just her
nature...)

\nw[Prae's voice]I've been keeping an eye on your situation from
over here, so I know what's going on. The island
you arrived at is the one we were aiming for. I've
been there before, so I understand.

\nw[Prae's voice]For now, let's head towards the temple. It's
located near the center of the island.

\nw[Prae's voice]That island is currently teeming with monsters.
The fact that there are no monsters near you right
now is almost like a miracle.

\nw[Prae's voice]The surface of the temple is protected by a
barrier, so it's not easy for monsters to get in.
If you can move, let's relocate right away.

\nw[Shia]Hmm... Ah, I think I can manage to walk. I don't
have much strength, though.

\nw[Taro]I see, then let's go to the center of the island.
It seems like this is our destination, and there
is a temple there.

\nw[Taro]It's tough for me to fight against monsters in my
current state...

\nw[Kuno]We've arrived on this island, right? Where should
we go?

\nw[Prae's voice]If we go straight, there is a temple. Both of them
are there.
\nw[Kuno]It seems like we should go straight, everyone.

\nw[Nonna]There doesn't seem to be any sign of monsters.
Let's leave the ship's security to the guys and go
pick up Taro.
